      "date": "2014-05-30 00:47:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n>it is already checked right in mdd_is_subdir->mdd_la_get. how the flag succeeded to disappear between the check and mdo_attr_get is a question.\n\nNo, it should check before mdd_is_subdir, see mdd_is_subdir->mdd_object_type->lu_object_attr-> LASSERT(lu_object_exists(o) != 0);",
